  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 35.23,
      "text": "Screen English and Fascinating Screen English Time"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.23,
      "end": 37.31,
      "text": "6월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.31,
      "end": 42.01,
      "text": "Benedict Cumberbatch, Michael Shannon, Nicholas Holt, G.A.N.A."
    },
    {
      "start": 42.01,
      "end": 43.39,
      "text": "The Current War!"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.61,
      "end": 45.47,
      "text": "Wow! Good Morning!"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.89,
      "end": 47.79,
      "text": "Good Morning, everyone! Top of the Morning!"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.03,
      "end": 48.25,
      "text": "Yeah!"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.69,
      "end": 50.03,
      "text": "Hi, Laura! Hi, GM Piers!"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.73,
      "end": 52.37,
      "text": "네, 근데 오늘이"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.37,
      "end": 54.27,
      "text": "It's the last day to watch this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 54.63,
      "end": 54.99,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.23,
      "end": 56.53,
      "text": "It's the end of the movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.85,
      "end": 58.15,
      "text": "What else is new?"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.65,
      "end": 59.53,
      "text": "그러게 말입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 59.69,
      "end": 62.37,
      "text": "Are you gonna miss Mr. Cumberbatch?"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.51,
      "end": 63.93,
      "text": "Yeah, sure."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.93,
      "end": 65.29,
      "text": "Yeah, 당연하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 65.53,
      "end": 66.25,
      "text": "Get over it."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.57,
      "end": 68.53,
      "text": "You're a happily married lady."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.13,
      "end": 69.85,
      "text": "You're fine."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.13,
      "end": 71.65,
      "text": "그거, 이거하고 좀 다른데."
    },
    {
      "start": 72.27,
      "end": 72.63,
      "text": "Oh, really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.99,
      "end": 74.83,
      "text": "다른가?"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.03,
      "end": 77.91,
      "text": "저는 항상 이렇게 마지막 주만 되면"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.91,
      "end": 81.53,
      "text": "이 영화의 아쉬움을 굉장히 많이 표현을 하는 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.17,
      "end": 83.51,
      "text": "이 마지막 장면을 보면"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.51,
      "end": 84.37,
      "text": "What did it say?"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.55,
      "end": 87.95,
      "text": "에디슨이 자기는 완전히 새로운 발명품을 만들겠다!"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.29,
      "end": 90.55,
      "text": "라고 웨스팅하우스에게 이야기를 하는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.55,
      "end": 91.45,
      "text": "A new invention"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.45,
      "end": 94.25,
      "text": "That will beat all other inventions"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.25,
      "end": 95.31,
      "text": "Yeah, 그게 바로"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.31,
      "end": 96.43,
      "text": "motion picture"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.43,
      "end": 97.71,
      "text": "이라는 거였거든요."
    },
    {
      "start": 98.43,
      "end": 99.51,
      "text": "네, motion picture는요."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.59,
      "end": 102.07,
      "text": "영화를 가리키는 옛 용어라고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.43,
      "end": 104.39,
      "text": "그래서 움직이는 사진 정도로"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.39,
      "end": 105.85,
      "text": "이해를 하실 수가 있는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.85,
      "end": 106.67,
      "text": "이"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.67,
      "end": 108.55,
      "text": "루이미엘 형제라는"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.55,
      "end": 110.05,
      "text": "사람들 들어보셨을 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.05,
      "end": 110.73,
      "text": "루이리 드미디에"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.73,
      "end": 112.45,
      "text": "It sounds very French."
    },
    {
      "start": 112.51,
      "end": 113.61,
      "text": "Yeah, they're French, aren't they?"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.65,
      "end": 114.27,
      "text": "French brothers."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.47,
      "end": 114.77,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.77,
      "end": 118.07,
      "text": "Oh, 그럼 프랑스어로 한번 발음해 주실 수 있나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.31,
      "end": 121.05,
      "text": "Well, I'm going to have to ask my friend 조승연."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.17,
      "end": 121.47,
      "text": "Oh!"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.67,
      "end": 122.49,
      "text": "프랑스 말 잘하더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.49,
      "end": 123.17,
      "text": "맞아요, 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.17,
      "end": 124.01,
      "text": "저는 못해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.21,
      "end": 125.45,
      "text": "아, 리미엘."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.67,
      "end": 127.83,
      "text": "우리는 굉장히 이 정도로 한번 발음해 볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.99,
      "end": 129.25,
      "text": "한글로 읽는 게 훨씬 편해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.27,
      "end": 129.63,
      "text": "알겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.79,
      "end": 130.57,
      "text": "리미엘 형제."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.57,
      "end": 131.17,
      "text": "리미엘 형제."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.17,
      "end": 133.87,
      "text": "Oh, 뭔가 클리어리하게 언뜻지는 되네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 133.93,
      "end": 134.79,
      "text": "Anyway, two brothers"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.79,
      "end": 137.03,
      "text": "who created the projector"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.03,
      "end": 139.61,
      "text": "and they used the projector with the camera"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.61,
      "end": 141.99,
      "text": "to make the first movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.99,
      "end": 144.19,
      "text": "and project it on a big screen"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.19,
      "end": 145.97,
      "text": "way back in 1895."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.01,
      "end": 149.93,
      "text": "And I saw a clip of this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.07,
      "end": 151.85,
      "text": "It was very simple."
    },
    {
      "start": 152.09,
      "end": 153.97,
      "text": "No words, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.19,
      "end": 155.23,
      "text": "Black and white."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.41,
      "end": 157.13,
      "text": "It was of a train moving."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.13,
      "end": 159.87,
      "text": "and I heard the people watching the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.87,
      "end": 161.25,
      "text": "were so surprised"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.25,
      "end": 163.13,
      "text": "they jumped out of their seats"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.13,
      "end": 165.11,
      "text": "because there was a train moving,"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.15,
      "end": 166.75,
      "text": "a moving train on a screen"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.75,
      "end": 168.89,
      "text": "and they thought it was coming towards them."
    },
    {
      "start": 169.27,
      "end": 169.55,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 170.21,
      "end": 172.61,
      "text": "이게 또 나중에 역사적으로 보면"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.61,
      "end": 175.39,
      "text": "이 에디슨하고 리미엘의 형제가요."
    },
    {
      "start": 175.87,
      "end": 176.91,
      "text": "동영상 특허?"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.25,
      "end": 178.19,
      "text": "그래서 좀 찾아보니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.19,
      "end": 180.23,
      "text": "Cinematography라고 해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.23,
      "end": 182.85,
      "text": "카메라 겸 영상기를 두고 경쟁을 했대요."
    },
    {
      "start": 182.87,
      "end": 184.13,
      "text": "아, Cinematography."
    },
    {
      "start": 185.53,
      "end": 186.31,
      "text": "바른 바른요."
    },
    {
      "start": 186.31,
      "end": 186.69,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.77,
      "end": 189.87,
      "text": "에디슨 competed with them as well, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.21,
      "end": 190.61,
      "text": "에디슨."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.73,
      "end": 190.93,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 191.05,
      "end": 193.45,
      "text": "그래서 또 다른 경쟁상들을 만나게 되는 거네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 193.55,
      "end": 193.67,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 193.73,
      "end": 195.11,
      "text": "There were several people involved"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.11,
      "end": 197.23,
      "text": "in creating movies,"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.53,
      "end": 198.33,
      "text": "motion pictures,"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.47,
      "end": 199.57,
      "text": "as we know them today."
    },
    {
      "start": 199.67,
      "end": 199.89,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 200.11,
      "end": 200.97,
      "text": "There was one guy"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.97,
      "end": 202.81,
      "text": "who just took a bunch of pictures"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.81,
      "end": 204.07,
      "text": "of a moving horse"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.07,
      "end": 205.79,
      "text": "and he put the pictures together"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.79,
      "end": 207.71,
      "text": "so it looked like the horse was moving."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.79,
      "end": 207.99,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.27,
      "end": 209.87,
      "text": "And many people contributed"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.87,
      "end": 211.61,
      "text": "to the wonderful movies"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.61,
      "end": 213.01,
      "text": "that we enjoy today,"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.25,
      "end": 214.69,
      "text": "including Mr. 에디슨."
    },
    {
      "start": 214.87,
      "end": 215.21,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.21,
      "end": 217.29,
      "text": "그래서 정말 이 발명에"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.29,
      "end": 219.31,
      "text": "끊임없는 경쟁을 했구나라는 것도"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.31,
      "end": 219.89,
      "text": "알게 됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.51,
      "end": 221.59,
      "text": "자, 일단 오늘 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.59,
      "end": 222.21,
      "text": "듣고 오겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 222.21,
      "end": 224.74,
      "text": "I'm working on something now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.86,
      "end": 226.06,
      "text": "something so new that"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.06,
      "end": 227.3,
      "text": "people will forget"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.3,
      "end": 228.68,
      "text": "that my name is ever associated"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.68,
      "end": 229.46,
      "text": "with electricity."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.74,
      "end": 232.2,
      "text": "I wonder if you know what it is yet."
    },
    {
      "start": 233.65,
      "end": 235.21,
      "text": "You know, I think the solution is"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.21,
      "end": 238.04,
      "text": "to divide the cost of the fence"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.04,
      "end": 240.48,
      "text": "where you could not build a fence"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.48,
      "end": 241.58,
      "text": "at all."
    },
    {
      "start": 241.58,
      "end": 244.12,
      "text": "Your garden would be twice as big,"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.06,
      "end": 245.56,
      "text": "wouldn't it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.0,
      "end": 246.22,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 247.78,
      "end": 248.86,
      "text": "Nothing else a pleasure."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.5,
      "end": 252.34,
      "text": "역시 우리 에디슨에게는요,"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.4,
      "end": 253.98,
      "text": "he had a lot of hidden cars."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.18,
      "end": 254.5,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.94,
      "end": 257.0,
      "text": "He has a lot of tricks up his sleeve."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.14,
      "end": 257.38,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.72,
      "end": 258.68,
      "text": "Yeah, he's gonna pull them out"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.68,
      "end": 259.54,
      "text": "one by one."
    },
    {
      "start": 259.6,
      "end": 260.3,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 260.3,
      "end": 262.64,
      "text": "전류 전쟁에서는 졌지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.64,
      "end": 263.86,
      "text": "그래도 곧바로"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.86,
      "end": 264.78,
      "text": "영화 사업으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.78,
      "end": 265.76,
      "text": "눈을 돌리게 되는"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.76,
      "end": 266.62,
      "text": "그런 에디슨의"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.62,
      "end": 268.02,
      "text": "우리가 살펴볼 수가 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 268.02,
      "end": 269.5,
      "text": "So he's still talking to"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.5,
      "end": 270.08,
      "text": "Westinghouse,"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.28,
      "end": 271.1,
      "text": "his rival."
    },
    {
      "start": 271.28,
      "end": 271.52,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 271.6,
      "end": 273.66,
      "text": "They met at the big Chicago fair,"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.88,
      "end": 274.72,
      "text": "the world fair."
    },
    {
      "start": 274.98,
      "end": 275.12,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.24,
      "end": 276.54,
      "text": "They ran into each other."
    },
    {
      "start": 276.64,
      "end": 277.62,
      "text": "우연히 많은 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 277.78,
      "end": 278.14,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.6,
      "end": 280.88,
      "text": "But they're having a very calm"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.88,
      "end": 282.34,
      "text": "and pleasant conversation."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.5,
      "end": 283.66,
      "text": "Yeah, I like that."
    },
    {
      "start": 283.9,
      "end": 285.1,
      "text": "So Westinghouse,"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.22,
      "end": 286.48,
      "text": "I think he wants to,"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.54,
      "end": 287.78,
      "text": "he's looking towards the future"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.78,
      "end": 289.78,
      "text": "and he wants to cooperate"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.78,
      "end": 291.0,
      "text": "with 에디슨."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.2,
      "end": 292.02,
      "text": "I wish I had someone"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.02,
      "end": 293.74,
      "text": "like Mr. Westinghouse."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.74,
      "end": 294.52,
      "text": "Oh, 진짜."
    },
    {
      "start": 294.86,
      "end": 295.88,
      "text": "이런 사람이 옆에 있으면"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.88,
      "end": 296.62,
      "text": "얼마나 좋을까"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.62,
      "end": 297.92,
      "text": "이런 생각을 하게 되더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.02,
      "end": 299.1,
      "text": "Let's work together, Laura."
    },
    {
      "start": 299.3,
      "end": 299.64,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 299.72,
      "end": 300.44,
      "text": "I have money."
    },
    {
      "start": 300.74,
      "end": 302.08,
      "text": "You have ideas."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.3,
      "end": 302.9,
      "text": "든든하다."
    },
    {
      "start": 303.28,
      "end": 303.84,
      "text": "Come on."
    },
    {
      "start": 303.98,
      "end": 305.76,
      "text": "We can be a dream team."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.86,
      "end": 306.34,
      "text": "맞습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 306.48,
      "end": 308.04,
      "text": "우리는 dream team 될 수 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 308.74,
      "end": 310.36,
      "text": "자, 어떤 단어들 들어볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 310.86,
      "end": 311.78,
      "text": "Working on."
    },
    {
      "start": 311.84,
      "end": 312.98,
      "text": "네, working on"
    },
    {
      "start": 312.98,
      "end": 314.34,
      "text": "이라는 표현이 들릴 건데"
    },
    {
      "start": 314.34,
      "end": 316.52,
      "text": "뭔가 일하고 있는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 316.52,
      "end": 317.66,
      "text": "착수하고 있다,"
    },
    {
      "start": 317.86,
      "end": 319.86,
      "text": "공들이고 있다라는 의미입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 319.96,
      "end": 321.14,
      "text": "What are you working on?"
    },
    {
      "start": 321.14,
      "end": 322.12,
      "text": "뭐 하고 있어?"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.2,
      "end": 324.78,
      "text": "Associated with"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.78,
      "end": 326.62,
      "text": "Associated with"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.62,
      "end": 327.48,
      "text": "라는 표현은"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.48,
      "end": 328.8,
      "text": "뭐뭐와 관련된"
    },
    {
      "start": 328.8,
      "end": 329.86,
      "text": "이라는 의미라는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.86,
      "end": 330.64,
      "text": "알고 계실 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.76,
      "end": 330.9,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 331.64,
      "end": 333.08,
      "text": "And the solution."
    },
    {
      "start": 333.38,
      "end": 334.38,
      "text": "네, solution"
    },
    {
      "start": 334.38,
      "end": 335.18,
      "text": "이라는 단어"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.18,
      "end": 336.12,
      "text": "딱 들으셨죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 336.34,
      "end": 337.02,
      "text": "The solution."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.38,
      "end": 338.02,
      "text": "해결책"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.02,
      "end": 339.12,
      "text": "이라는 의미도"
    },
    {
      "start": 339.12,
      "end": 340.46,
      "text": "들으실 수가 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 341.2,
      "end": 341.8,
      "text": "자, 이 내용"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.8,
      "end": 342.62,
      "text": "집중하시면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.62,
      "end": 343.52,
      "text": "한 번 더 들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 343.52,
      "end": 346.12,
      "text": "I'm working on something now."
    },
    {
      "start": 346.26,
      "end": 347.24,
      "text": "Something so new"
    },
    {
      "start": 347.24,
      "end": 348.66,
      "text": "that people will forget"
    },
    {
      "start": 348.66,
      "end": 349.52,
      "text": "that my name is ever"
    },
    {
      "start": 349.52,
      "end": 350.84,
      "text": "associated with electricity."
    },
    {
      "start": 352.13,
      "end": 352.91,
      "text": "I wonder if you know"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.91,
      "end": 353.57,
      "text": "what it is yet."
    },
    {
      "start": 355.04,
      "end": 355.54,
      "text": "You know, I think"
    },
    {
      "start": 355.54,
      "end": 356.58,
      "text": "the solution is"
    },
    {
      "start": 356.58,
      "end": 358.8,
      "text": "to divide the cost"
    },
    {
      "start": 358.8,
      "end": 359.42,
      "text": "of the fence."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.2,
      "end": 361.06,
      "text": "Or you could not"
    },
    {
      "start": 361.06,
      "end": 361.86,
      "text": "build a fence"
    },
    {
      "start": 361.86,
      "end": 362.96,
      "text": "at all."
    },
    {
      "start": 363.7,
      "end": 364.2,
      "text": "Your garden"
    },
    {
      "start": 364.2,
      "end": 365.52,
      "text": "would be twice as big."
    },
    {
      "start": 366.43,
      "end": 366.93,
      "text": "Wouldn't it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 367.37,
      "end": 367.59,
      "text": "Tom?"
    },
    {
      "start": 369.13,
      "end": 369.81,
      "text": "Nothing else."
    },
    {
      "start": 369.87,
      "end": 370.21,
      "text": "A pleasure."
    },
    {
      "start": 370.21,
      "end": 375.14,
      "text": "I can feel"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.14,
      "end": 375.64,
      "text": "the freedom"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.64,
      "end": 376.76,
      "text": "of the winner here."
    },
    {
      "start": 376.9,
      "end": 377.2,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 377.48,
      "end": 377.74,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 377.96,
      "end": 378.46,
      "text": "And Edison"
    },
    {
      "start": 378.46,
      "end": 379.72,
      "text": "is not interested."
    },
    {
      "start": 380.58,
      "end": 381.64,
      "text": "Yeah, he does."
    },
    {
      "start": 381.88,
      "end": 382.88,
      "text": "He's offering"
    },
    {
      "start": 382.88,
      "end": 383.46,
      "text": "to work"
    },
    {
      "start": 383.46,
      "end": 384.92,
      "text": "with the loser."
    },
    {
      "start": 385.1,
      "end": 385.3,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 385.4,
      "end": 385.72,
      "text": "Edison."
    },
    {
      "start": 385.98,
      "end": 386.4,
      "text": "Loser."
    },
    {
      "start": 386.5,
      "end": 387.74,
      "text": "Very magnanimous."
    },
    {
      "start": 388.02,
      "end": 389.02,
      "text": "Well, he's not"
    },
    {
      "start": 389.02,
      "end": 389.68,
      "text": "really a loser."
    },
    {
      "start": 389.9,
      "end": 391.18,
      "text": "But in this contest,"
    },
    {
      "start": 391.38,
      "end": 392.24,
      "text": "he lost."
    },
    {
      "start": 392.4,
      "end": 392.6,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 393.36,
      "end": 394.4,
      "text": "하지만 Edison"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.4,
      "end": 395.92,
      "text": "이 제안에"
    },
    {
      "start": 395.92,
      "end": 396.96,
      "text": "동의하지 않고"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.96,
      "end": 398.1,
      "text": "또 도도하게"
    },
    {
      "start": 398.1,
      "end": 399.0,
      "text": "자기 갈 길을"
    },
    {
      "start": 399.0,
      "end": 399.66,
      "text": "걸어간다는"
    },
    {
      "start": 399.66,
      "end": 400.3,
      "text": "이야기입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 400.3,
      "end": 401.9,
      "text": "그 마지막 대사는"
    },
    {
      "start": 401.9,
      "end": 402.28,
      "text": "그냥"
    },
    {
      "start": 402.28,
      "end": 403.18,
      "text": "Bye Bye"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.18,
      "end": 403.62,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 404.12,
      "end": 404.86,
      "text": "이란 말이었죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 404.96,
      "end": 405.88,
      "text": "네, 어떤 내용인지"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.88,
      "end": 407.14,
      "text": "너무너무 궁금한데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 407.26,
      "end": 407.84,
      "text": "살펴보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.98,
      "end": 409.82,
      "text": "I'm working on"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.82,
      "end": 410.88,
      "text": "something new."
    },
    {
      "start": 411.02,
      "end": 412.06,
      "text": "오, Edison이"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.06,
      "end": 412.82,
      "text": "하는 말이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 413.14,
      "end": 413.94,
      "text": "I'm working on"
    },
    {
      "start": 413.94,
      "end": 414.98,
      "text": "something new."
    },
    {
      "start": 415.46,
      "end": 416.1,
      "text": "나는 뭔가"
    },
    {
      "start": 416.1,
      "end": 417.28,
      "text": "새로운 일을"
    },
    {
      "start": 417.28,
      "end": 418.42,
      "text": "하고 있는 중입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 419.7,
      "end": 420.72,
      "text": "라이블 듣기에"
    },
    {
      "start": 420.72,
      "end": 421.88,
      "text": "오, something new."
    },
    {
      "start": 421.98,
      "end": 422.86,
      "text": "What is it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 422.94,
      "end": 423.86,
      "text": "Tell me."
    },
    {
      "start": 424.08,
      "end": 424.52,
      "text": "지금 막"
    },
    {
      "start": 424.52,
      "end": 425.88,
      "text": "네가 지자마자"
    },
    {
      "start": 425.88,
      "end": 426.24,
      "text": "곧바로"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.24,
      "end": 426.8,
      "text": "새로운 일을"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.8,
      "end": 427.5,
      "text": "하고 있는 중이라고?"
    },
    {
      "start": 427.8,
      "end": 428.58,
      "text": "라는 반응을"
    },
    {
      "start": 428.58,
      "end": 429.36,
      "text": "할 수 있을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 429.36,
      "end": 431.28,
      "text": "Something so new"
    },
    {
      "start": 431.28,
      "end": 432.16,
      "text": "that people"
    },
    {
      "start": 432.16,
      "end": 432.84,
      "text": "will forget"
    },
    {
      "start": 432.84,
      "end": 433.38,
      "text": "my name"
    },
    {
      "start": 433.38,
      "end": 434.12,
      "text": "was ever"
    },
    {
      "start": 434.12,
      "end": 434.78,
      "text": "associated"
    },
    {
      "start": 434.78,
      "end": 436.04,
      "text": "with electricity."
    },
    {
      "start": 436.54,
      "end": 437.1,
      "text": "Wow,"
    },
    {
      "start": 437.28,
      "end": 437.82,
      "text": "I can already"
    },
    {
      "start": 437.82,
      "end": 438.62,
      "text": "feel confident"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.62,
      "end": 439.16,
      "text": "in his way"
    },
    {
      "start": 439.16,
      "end": 439.7,
      "text": "of speaking."
    },
    {
      "start": 439.9,
      "end": 440.58,
      "text": "He sounds"
    },
    {
      "start": 440.58,
      "end": 441.7,
      "text": "really confident."
    },
    {
      "start": 441.78,
      "end": 442.18,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 442.34,
      "end": 443.02,
      "text": "And I"
    },
    {
      "start": 443.02,
      "end": 443.96,
      "text": "cannot wait"
    },
    {
      "start": 443.96,
      "end": 444.64,
      "text": "to find out"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.64,
      "end": 444.96,
      "text": "what"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.96,
      "end": 445.6,
      "text": "what is he"
    },
    {
      "start": 445.6,
      "end": 446.24,
      "text": "working on"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.24,
      "end": 446.96,
      "text": "if I"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.96,
      "end": 447.12,
      "text": "were"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.12,
      "end": 447.46,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 447.46,
      "end": 448.14,
      "text": "Westinghouse."
    },
    {
      "start": 448.14,
      "end": 449.48,
      "text": "이런 방식으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 449.48,
      "end": 450.22,
      "text": "이야기를 하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 450.22,
      "end": 451.32,
      "text": "자부심이"
    },
    {
      "start": 451.32,
      "end": 452.28,
      "text": "너무 넘치니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.28,
      "end": 453.44,
      "text": "도대체 뭔데?"
    },
    {
      "start": 453.86,
      "end": 454.58,
      "text": "도대체 뭔데?"
    },
    {
      "start": 454.66,
      "end": 454.96,
      "text": "막 이렇게"
    },
    {
      "start": 454.96,
      "end": 455.32,
      "text": "물어보고"
    },
    {
      "start": 455.32,
      "end": 455.96,
      "text": "싶을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 456.46,
      "end": 456.94,
      "text": "에디슨이"
    },
    {
      "start": 456.94,
      "end": 457.52,
      "text": "뭐라고 했냐면"
    },
    {
      "start": 457.52,
      "end": 458.96,
      "text": "something so new."
    },
    {
      "start": 459.3,
      "end": 459.58,
      "text": "뭔가"
    },
    {
      "start": 459.58,
      "end": 460.7,
      "text": "너무 새로워서"
    },
    {
      "start": 460.7,
      "end": 461.54,
      "text": "that people"
    },
    {
      "start": 461.54,
      "end": 462.34,
      "text": "will forget"
    },
    {
      "start": 462.34,
      "end": 463.14,
      "text": "my name"
    },
    {
      "start": 463.14,
      "end": 463.76,
      "text": "사람들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 463.76,
      "end": 464.82,
      "text": "나의 이름을"
    },
    {
      "start": 464.82,
      "end": 466.14,
      "text": "잊어버릴"
    },
    {
      "start": 466.14,
      "end": 467.42,
      "text": "정도일 거라는 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.52,
      "end": 468.06,
      "text": "Was ever"
    },
    {
      "start": 468.06,
      "end": 469.32,
      "text": "associated with"
    },
    {
      "start": 469.32,
      "end": 470.06,
      "text": "electricity"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.06,
      "end": 470.96,
      "text": "라고 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.96,
      "end": 472.72,
      "text": "내 이름이"
    },
    {
      "start": 472.72,
      "end": 474.06,
      "text": "이 전류하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 474.06,
      "end": 475.52,
      "text": "연관이 되었다라는"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.52,
      "end": 476.26,
      "text": "것조차도"
    },
    {
      "start": 476.26,
      "end": 477.14,
      "text": "잊어버릴 수"
    },
    {
      "start": 477.14,
      "end": 477.74,
      "text": "있을 정도로"
    },
    {
      "start": 477.74,
      "end": 478.56,
      "text": "뭔가 새로운"
    },
    {
      "start": 478.56,
      "end": 479.02,
      "text": "일을"
    },
    {
      "start": 479.02,
      "end": 479.44,
      "text": "내가 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 479.44,
      "end": 480.44,
      "text": "있다라는 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 497.6,
      "end": 498.92,
      "text": "탁월한 선택이네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 499.34,
      "end": 500.36,
      "text": "이렇게 생각을 하는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 500.36,
      "end": 501.5,
      "text": "마음이 편할 수도 있겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 506.26,
      "end": 513.48,
      "text": "이미 그게 뭔지"
    },
    {
      "start": 513.48,
      "end": 514.32,
      "text": "알고 있는지"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.32,
      "end": 515.24,
      "text": "궁금한데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 515.32,
      "end": 516.4,
      "text": "Oftentimes inventors"
    },
    {
      "start": 516.4,
      "end": 517.24,
      "text": "they have many"
    },
    {
      "start": 517.24,
      "end": 519.1,
      "text": "really abstract ideas."
    },
    {
      "start": 519.58,
      "end": 520.28,
      "text": "They don't even know"
    },
    {
      "start": 520.28,
      "end": 521.34,
      "text": "exactly what they are."
    },
    {
      "start": 521.76,
      "end": 522.42,
      "text": "So Westinghouse"
    },
    {
      "start": 522.42,
      "end": 523.7,
      "text": "is being very practical."
    },
    {
      "start": 524.34,
      "end": 524.76,
      "text": "그거 뭐"
    },
    {
      "start": 524.76,
      "end": 526.38,
      "text": "뭔지도 안단 말이야?"
    },
    {
      "start": 526.52,
      "end": 527.44,
      "text": "I wonder if you"
    },
    {
      "start": 527.44,
      "end": 527.86,
      "text": "even know"
    },
    {
      "start": 527.86,
      "end": 528.86,
      "text": "what you're talking about."
    },
    {
      "start": 528.98,
      "end": 529.4,
      "text": "그러게."
    },
    {
      "start": 529.54,
      "end": 530.64,
      "text": "추상적인 게 아니라"
    },
    {
      "start": 530.64,
      "end": 531.82,
      "text": "굉장히 구체적으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 531.82,
      "end": 532.72,
      "text": "알고 있다는 것이"
    },
    {
      "start": 532.72,
      "end": 533.94,
      "text": "정말 신기하구만"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.94,
      "end": 534.82,
      "text": "궁금하구만"
    },
    {
      "start": 534.82,
      "end": 535.8,
      "text": "이라고 이야기한다고"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.8,
      "end": 536.86,
      "text": "생각하시면 될 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 537.28,
      "end": 538.0,
      "text": "You know"
    },
    {
      "start": 538.0,
      "end": 540.76,
      "text": "I think the solution is"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.76,
      "end": 542.94,
      "text": "Then he got to the point."
    },
    {
      "start": 543.3,
      "end": 543.98,
      "text": "본론으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 543.98,
      "end": 545.14,
      "text": "탁 들어가 버리는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 545.9,
      "end": 546.32,
      "text": "계속해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 546.32,
      "end": 547.16,
      "text": "Westinghouse가"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.16,
      "end": 547.68,
      "text": "에디슨에게"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.68,
      "end": 548.68,
      "text": "질문을 하는 건데"
    },
    {
      "start": 548.68,
      "end": 549.28,
      "text": "You know"
    },
    {
      "start": 549.28,
      "end": 551.52,
      "text": "I think the solution is"
    },
    {
      "start": 551.52,
      "end": 553.9,
      "text": "당신도 알다시피"
    },
    {
      "start": 553.9,
      "end": 555.44,
      "text": "해결책은 말이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 556.44,
      "end": 557.84,
      "text": "To divide"
    },
    {
      "start": 557.84,
      "end": 559.46,
      "text": "the cost of the fence."
    },
    {
      "start": 560.14,
      "end": 561.5,
      "text": "It's an example."
    },
    {
      "start": 561.7,
      "end": 563.58,
      "text": "A figurative example."
    },
    {
      "start": 563.58,
      "end": 565.22,
      "text": "To divide"
    },
    {
      "start": 565.22,
      "end": 566.36,
      "text": "the cost of"
    },
    {
      "start": 566.36,
      "end": 567.0,
      "text": "the fence"
    },
    {
      "start": 567.0,
      "end": 567.64,
      "text": "라고 했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 567.8,
      "end": 568.16,
      "text": "Fence?"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.24,
      "end": 569.32,
      "text": "They're not building a fence."
    },
    {
      "start": 569.54,
      "end": 570.34,
      "text": "What's this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.72,
      "end": 572.22,
      "text": "Fence라는 단어는"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.22,
      "end": 572.52,
      "text": "우리가"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.52,
      "end": 575.72,
      "text": "많은 어르신분들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 575.72,
      "end": 577.1,
      "text": "휀쓰"
    },
    {
      "start": 577.1,
      "end": 577.58,
      "text": "아"
    },
    {
      "start": 577.58,
      "end": 578.68,
      "text": "그렇게 발음하세요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.9,
      "end": 578.92,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.92,
      "end": 579.94,
      "text": "옛날에는 많이"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.94,
      "end": 580.58,
      "text": "휀쓰"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.58,
      "end": 581.92,
      "text": "이렇게 발음을 하시는 분들을"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.92,
      "end": 582.88,
      "text": "제가 몇 번 들었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 582.88,
      "end": 584.12,
      "text": "우리 말도 휀쓰"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.12,
      "end": 584.62,
      "text": "하는구나."
    },
    {
      "start": 584.98,
      "end": 585.1,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.1,
      "end": 586.04,
      "text": "울타리"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.04,
      "end": 587.24,
      "text": "라는 의미입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 587.36,
      "end": 587.68,
      "text": "울타리"
    },
    {
      "start": 587.68,
      "end": 588.48,
      "text": "Fence"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.48,
      "end": 590.34,
      "text": "이 울타리를"
    },
    {
      "start": 590.34,
      "end": 592.26,
      "text": "나누는"
    },
    {
      "start": 592.26,
      "end": 593.3,
      "text": "비용을"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.3,
      "end": 594.38,
      "text": "나누자라는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 595.32,
      "end": 595.82,
      "text": "Half half"
    },
    {
      "start": 595.82,
      "end": 596.76,
      "text": "Let's split the cost."
    },
    {
      "start": 597.16,
      "end": 597.74,
      "text": "You pay half"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.74,
      "end": 598.34,
      "text": "I'll pay half."
    },
    {
      "start": 598.44,
      "end": 599.6,
      "text": "50-50"
    },
    {
      "start": 599.6,
      "end": 600.02,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.02,
      "end": 601.14,
      "text": "Or"
    },
    {
      "start": 601.14,
      "end": 602.68,
      "text": "You cannot build"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.68,
      "end": 603.7,
      "text": "a fence at all."
    },
    {
      "start": 604.24,
      "end": 604.64,
      "text": "혹은"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.64,
      "end": 605.74,
      "text": "You cannot build"
    },
    {
      "start": 605.74,
      "end": 606.78,
      "text": "a fence at all"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.78,
      "end": 607.32,
      "text": "이라고 했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 607.32,
      "end": 607.78,
      "text": "아니면"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.78,
      "end": 609.04,
      "text": "당신이 그 울타리를"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.04,
      "end": 610.86,
      "text": "전혀 만들지 않을 수도 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 610.86,
      "end": 611.78,
      "text": "라고 이야기를 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 611.94,
      "end": 612.46,
      "text": "Basically"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.46,
      "end": 613.74,
      "text": "You need me"
    },
    {
      "start": 613.74,
      "end": 614.22,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.22,
      "end": 615.58,
      "text": "He's talking by metaphor."
    },
    {
      "start": 615.88,
      "end": 616.2,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.2,
      "end": 617.34,
      "text": "You need my money"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.34,
      "end": 617.86,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.86,
      "end": 618.9,
      "text": "To invent"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.9,
      "end": 620.18,
      "text": "the next great thing."
    },
    {
      "start": 621.14,
      "end": 622.33,
      "text": "Your garden"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.33,
      "end": 624.23,
      "text": "would be twice as big."
    },
    {
      "start": 624.43,
      "end": 624.97,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.97,
      "end": 626.01,
      "text": "Wouldn't it, Tom?"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.21,
      "end": 626.83,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.83,
      "end": 627.99,
      "text": "Your garden"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.99,
      "end": 629.33,
      "text": "당신의 garden은"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.33,
      "end": 629.85,
      "text": "정원은"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.85,
      "end": 631.41,
      "text": "would be twice as big"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.41,
      "end": 632.59,
      "text": "한 두 배로"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.59,
      "end": 633.71,
      "text": "커질 수도 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 633.91,
      "end": 634.81,
      "text": "Wouldn't it, Tom?"
    },
    {
      "start": 634.81,
      "end": 635.57,
      "text": "이라고 했거든요."
    },
    {
      "start": 635.85,
      "end": 636.89,
      "text": "안 그런가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 637.05,
      "end": 637.47,
      "text": "Tom?"
    },
    {
      "start": 637.61,
      "end": 638.05,
      "text": "이라고 했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 638.17,
      "end": 638.45,
      "text": "Tom"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.45,
      "end": 638.47,
      "text": "Tom"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.47,
      "end": 639.29,
      "text": "Very 친근하게"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.29,
      "end": 639.59,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.59,
      "end": 641.09,
      "text": "He's calling his nickname"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.09,
      "end": 641.41,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.61,
      "end": 641.95,
      "text": "Tom"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.95,
      "end": 642.87,
      "text": "Well it's"
    },
    {
      "start": 642.87,
      "end": 643.17,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.17,
      "end": 644.21,
      "text": "Tom is"
    },
    {
      "start": 644.21,
      "end": 646.45,
      "text": "Tom is Tom"
    },
    {
      "start": 646.45,
      "end": 646.85,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 646.85,
      "end": 647.75,
      "text": "He probably wants"
    },
    {
      "start": 647.75,
      "end": 648.35,
      "text": "to get along"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.35,
      "end": 648.93,
      "text": "with Edison"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.93,
      "end": 649.55,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 649.55,
      "end": 651.43,
      "text": "He wants to partner up"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.43,
      "end": 651.81,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.81,
      "end": 653.01,
      "text": "아주 조심스럽고"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.01,
      "end": 653.99,
      "text": "또 젠틀하게"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.99,
      "end": 655.43,
      "text": "Let's work together"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.43,
      "end": 656.71,
      "text": "이 이야기를 하고 있는"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.71,
      "end": 657.37,
      "text": "상황입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 658.43,
      "end": 659.43,
      "text": "And Mr. Edison"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.43,
      "end": 659.81,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.81,
      "end": 661.37,
      "text": "If nothing else"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.37,
      "end": 662.29,
      "text": "A pleasure"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.29,
      "end": 663.93,
      "text": "A very cold"
    },
    {
      "start": 663.93,
      "end": 664.49,
      "text": "굉장히"
    },
    {
      "start": 664.49,
      "end": 665.41,
      "text": "chic하면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.41,
      "end": 666.05,
      "text": "Howdy"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.05,
      "end": 666.83,
      "text": "도도하게"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.83,
      "end": 667.23,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 667.31,
      "end": 668.65,
      "text": "아주 냉정한 느낌"
    },
    {
      "start": 668.65,
      "end": 669.27,
      "text": "아 그러게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.27,
      "end": 670.23,
      "text": "If nothing else"
    },
    {
      "start": 670.23,
      "end": 670.95,
      "text": "A pleasure"
    },
    {
      "start": 670.95,
      "end": 672.33,
      "text": "딴 거 없으면"
    },
    {
      "start": 672.33,
      "end": 673.57,
      "text": "이만 가보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.57,
      "end": 674.53,
      "text": "이런 내용입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.53,
      "end": 675.19,
      "text": "아 바로 그 느낌"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.19,
      "end": 675.63,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.63,
      "end": 677.13,
      "text": "엄청난 대안했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.13,
      "end": 678.39,
      "text": "이만 가볼게"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.39,
      "end": 680.35,
      "text": "딴 거 없으면"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.35,
      "end": 680.99,
      "text": "전 이만"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.99,
      "end": 681.75,
      "text": "실례하겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 681.75,
      "end": 683.13,
      "text": "라고 이야기를 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.13,
      "end": 684.43,
      "text": "아주 매력적인"
    },
    {
      "start": 684.43,
      "end": 685.41,
      "text": "성격을 가지고 있죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.41,
      "end": 685.91,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.91,
      "end": 686.69,
      "text": "Strong man"
    },
    {
      "start": 686.69,
      "end": 687.51,
      "text": "He has confidence"
    },
    {
      "start": 687.51,
      "end": 687.93,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 687.93,
      "end": 688.89,
      "text": "We'll see what happens"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.89,
      "end": 689.51,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 689.51,
      "end": 690.59,
      "text": "아 우리 이 내용"
    },
    {
      "start": 690.59,
      "end": 691.29,
      "text": "떠올리시면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 691.29,
      "end": 692.27,
      "text": "한 번 더 들어보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.27,
      "end": 694.84,
      "text": "I'm working on something now"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.84,
      "end": 695.98,
      "text": "or something so new"
    },
    {
      "start": 695.98,
      "end": 697.42,
      "text": "that people will forget"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.42,
      "end": 698.8,
      "text": "my name is ever associated"
    },
    {
      "start": 698.8,
      "end": 699.6,
      "text": "with electricity"
    },
    {
      "start": 699.6,
      "end": 701.64,
      "text": "I wonder if you know"
    },
    {
      "start": 701.64,
      "end": 702.36,
      "text": "what it is yet"
    },
    {
      "start": 702.36,
      "end": 704.27,
      "text": "You know I think"
    },
    {
      "start": 704.27,
      "end": 705.33,
      "text": "the solution is"
    },
    {
      "start": 705.33,
      "end": 707.53,
      "text": "to divide the cost"
    },
    {
      "start": 707.53,
      "end": 708.17,
      "text": "of the fence"
    },
    {
      "start": 708.17,
      "end": 709.77,
      "text": "or you could not"
    },
    {
      "start": 709.77,
      "end": 710.59,
      "text": "build a fence"
    },
    {
      "start": 710.59,
      "end": 711.73,
      "text": "at all"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.73,
      "end": 713.29,
      "text": "Your garden would be"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.29,
      "end": 714.27,
      "text": "twice as big"
    },
    {
      "start": 714.27,
      "end": 716.04,
      "text": "wouldn't it"
    },
    {
      "start": 716.04,
      "end": 716.4,
      "text": "Tom"
    },
    {
      "start": 716.4,
      "end": 718.55,
      "text": "Nothing else"
    },
    {
      "start": 718.55,
      "end": 718.97,
      "text": "A pleasure"
    },
    {
      "start": 718.97,
      "end": 721.66,
      "text": "와 우리"
    },
    {
      "start": 721.66,
      "end": 722.42,
      "text": "Current War"
    },
    {
      "start": 722.42,
      "end": 723.38,
      "text": "로 보는 이"
    },
    {
      "start": 723.38,
      "end": 724.22,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬는"
    },
    {
      "start": 724.22,
